    <body>
        <h1>{$node_name}</h1>
        <p align="Justify"></p>

        <div style="font-size: 15px;"><b>Billing Report</b><br /></div>
        <br />
        <p>Billing Reports show a complete report of calls with respect a rate established in "Billing Rates".</p>
        <p>The fields in this reports are:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Date            ->   Initial date of call</li>
            <li>Rate Applied    ->   Name of Rate applied</li>
            <li>Rate Value      ->   Rate value by minutes</li>
            <li>Source          ->   Number or source</li>
            <li>Destination     ->   Destination Number</li>
            <li>Dst. Channel    ->   Channel Destination(Example: DAHDI/1)</li>
            <li>Account Code    ->   Code of account extension</li>
            <li>Duration        ->   Duration in seconds of calls</li>
            <li>Cost            ->   Cost of call</li>
            <li>Summary Cost    ->   Sum of all calls by cost field</li>
        </ul>
        <br />
        <div><img src="../modules/{$node_id}/images/help_billing_report.png" border="0"></div>
        <div align="center"><p>Figure 1</p></div>
        <br />
    </body>
